{"tid":361590,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【國泰業績】中期勁蝕逾20億遠遜預期 燃油對沖虧損32億！","createTime":"2017-08-16T09:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T05:26:25.000Z","uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40dc859034335ab69b8037adc12894a5cbcd28a4","tid":361590,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"一反常態，國泰（0293）把中期業績的公布時間由中午延至收市後，至剛剛終公布業績報告。國泰上半年收益微升0.45至458.58億元，但淨虧損卻高達20.51億元，去年同期則賺3.53億元，同時遠差於市場預期的蝕5億元，每股虧損52.1仙，不派中期息。<br />\n<br />\n至於過去一直纏繞國泰的燃油對沖，國泰上半年燃油對沖虧損高達32.37億元，但已較去年同期的44.9億元少。另外，國泰上半年亦錄得多項一次性的財務影響，包括歐洲委員會於三月對國泰徵收4.98億元的罰款、5月裁員所帶來的2.24億元離職補償等成本。<br />\n<br />\n國泰主席史樂山於業績報告中表示，航空業的根本性結構轉變持續影響集團旗下航空公司的經營環境，而國泰業績疲弱主要由於與其他航空公司之間的激烈競爭，及油價上漲、港元走強，及飛機維修成本上升等。<br />\n<br />\n國泰上半年的客運收益按年減少3.9%至321.05億元，可載客量增加1.1%，反映特拉維夫航線的推出及其他航線的班次增加，運載率上升0.2個百分點至84.7%，但收益率下跌5.2%，反映所有等級客艙均競爭激烈，以及以其他貨幣賺取的收益面對港元走強的不利影響。<br />\n<br />\n期內貨運收益則按年增長11.7%至105.15億元，可載貨量增加<br />\n<br />\n2.3%，運載率上升4個百分點至66.2%，載貨噸數增加11.5%，收益率同升4.4%。<br />\n<br />\n若不計燃油對沖的影響，國泰上半年的燃油成本按年增加33.4%，反映平均油價上升31.5%及耗油量增加1.6%。燃油成本上半年則佔整體營業成本30.4%。<br />\n<br />\n國泰全日收報11.7元，升0.86%。<a href=\"http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1502872196825&amp;issue=20170816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1502872196825%26issue%3D20170816&d=KvtloBbkJC6H0RGqyDvczC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1def12e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1502872196825&amp;issue=20170816</a>"},{"pid":"145203a04d57889fc1531dedb1c7647ec792069e","tid":361590,"uid":102091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1816c219efef5bc586f2a67ab0ca0e8c306b9e1","tid":361590,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:38:59.000Z","msg":"等入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb6242dcbb1a3f42c2bde77d51f30a1a1a07535","tid":361590,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打仲敢入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be774319e252464a1bcff124242ab38cc47fbf69","tid":361590,"uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:45:04.000Z","msg":"等俾支那收購"},{"pid":"a157d6adc3f47bad004cdacd524b24764da29afb","tid":361590,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:45:35.000Z","msg":"跌到夠殘都可以諗諗"},{"pid":"4e3d1a7277c4f52af39abbdc4dd77a1e5f85f2ed","tid":361590,"uid":10949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:26:28.000Z","msg":"今日開市跌10%係咪基本？"},{"pid":"5f7c1a221bfeb802a333f563a30f0c05c90122fb","tid":361590,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:45:12.000Z","msg":"屌點解會急升架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb5a4e47134569c624b01acc7a65a8b3ed508bf","tid":361590,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:52:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日開市跌10%係咪基本？</blockquote><br />\n國泰航空(00293)<br />\n<br />\n現價\t12.180\t最高價\t12.200<br />\n升跌(%)\t0.480(+4.10%)\t最低價\t11.70"},{"pid":"3faa5f579ef8747d7208d8ff1d75f2a6524de322","tid":361590,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:09:18.000Z","msg":"升啦升啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b570d2eafd2a8e676eff8e8948ff811fa6a8c973","tid":361590,"uid":123328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌點解會急升架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大戶做野唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/